maximum effect seen in events whose lightcurves are consistent\nwith a point-source lens, which includes the majority of microlensed bulge\ndwarfs published so far.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2009 20:00:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
